  "title": "PMO MANAGER",
  "description": "<p><br>\nPosition: PMO<br>\n<br>\nExperience: Freshers<br>\n<br>\nEducation Background: IT/Computer Science<br>\n<br>\nKeys Skills: Project Coordinator, Resource Management, Budget Management, Document Minutes Of Meetings(MoM), MS Project, Zoom and Microsoft Teams<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\nRole and Responsibilities:<br>\n<br>\n· Support project manager on tracking project progress, risk escalation and report on key performance metrics.<br>\n<br>\n· Support the renewal of project contracts and approval.<br>\n<br>\n· Support project timeline, status updates in SAP, and submission of Project Implementation Review (PIR).<br>\n<br>\n· Resource management – coordinating with departmental PMO on tracking time clocking, managing reports on HC and FTE, MRF utilization and tracking augment resources.<br>\n<br>\n· Serve as the point of contact for project finance administration (e.g., track and report funding utilisation and expiry management).<br>\n<br>\n· Manage knowledge base for processes, governance, and policy.<br>\n<br>\n· Maintain an inventory of project assets and versioning.<br>\n<br>\n· Deliver efficient and effective secretariat and administrative support (e.g., stakeholder coordination, manage meeting logistics and minuting) for Tech team.<br>\n<br>\n· Schedule meetings for the Tech team, document and manage meeting minutes.<br>\n<br>\n· Serves as a Business Analyst on tech deliverables.<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\nRequirements / Qualifications:<br>\n<br>\n· Degree in computer science or related field.<br>\n<br>\n· Proactive and dedicated individual with strong multi-tasking capabilities and attention to details.<br>\n<br>\no Ability to build and maintain relationships with a wide array of people at both junior and senior levels.<br>\n<br>\no High competency levels in project management tools and video conferencing tools e.g. MS Project, Zoom and Microsoft Teams.<br>\n<br>\no Knowledge of project management methodologies (e.g. Agile) o Experience in healthcare, data analytics &amp;/or research industries will be added advantage.</p>",
